msgctxt "product_positioning.self_hosting.operator_pass.donating_with_perks_smaller_space"
msgid ""
"Think of the optional {operator_pass} like donating with perks: you help keep {product_name} going and get the {operators} community, a smaller place where self-hosters and the {product_name} team can help when you get stuck, hear your ideas, and discuss feedback before it gets buried on {github}."
msgstr ""
"可以把可选的 {operator_pass} 看作带有福利的捐赠：你帮助 {product_name} 持续运转，并加入 {operators} 社区。这里是一个更小的空间，当你卡住时，其他自托管者和 {product_name} 团队可以提供帮助，也能听到你的想法，并在反馈被 {github} 淹没之前一起讨论。"

